        dc:description           "FIGURE 3. Female genitalia of Adustonotus graziae sp. nov.: A–B, E–F: genital plates; C–D: internal genitalia.A–B. posterior view; C. internal genitalia; D. Magnification of capsula seminalis; E–F. Posteroventral view. (aaf: anterior annular flange; cs: capsula seminalis; dr = ductus receptaculi; gcVIII: gonocoxites VIII; gcIX: gonocoxites IX; laVIII: laterotergites VIII laIX: laterotergites IX; paf: posterior annular flange; pi: pars intermedialis; rs: ring sclerites; stg: secondary thickenings of gonapophyses IX, va: vesicular area). Scale bars: 0.5mm." ;
