<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4692325>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. Bayesian Inference consensus tree based on the analysis of four molecular markers and morphological characters for 25 species of Adustonotus and related carpocorines. Numbers close to nodes are respectively Bayesian posterior probability / Maximum-Likelihood bootstrap support.Only nodal support above PP = 0.5 or BS = 50 were collapsed (“*” indicates uninformed value). A–C Dorsal habitus. A. Adustonotus graziae sp. nov.; B. Adustonotus latus (Dallas); C. Adustonotus grandis (Rolston). Scale bars: 5mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4692325/files/figure.png" .

